Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,《纸牌屋》前情提要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把包放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put down the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,放下包  把手放在头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put down the bag and place your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,站住别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为塔斯克此刻不是在谋划下一波进攻吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think Tusk isn't planning his next attack even as we speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该进攻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time we go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那赌场  我们尽快曝光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The casino. We go public as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,冯和塔斯克有关系 塔斯克与总统有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng has ties to Tusk. Tusk has ties to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我和这完全没关系  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with it, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在电话这头都闻得到谎言的臭气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can smell the horseshit through the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生 你能给我们讲一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, would you walk us through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你和雷蒙德·塔斯克的关系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your history with Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在人人都是靶子了 包括我自己在内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone is fair game now. Including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等我进监狱了来探视我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come and visit me when I'm in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大概六小时前  两艘中国驱逐舰进入了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two Chinese destroyers entered waters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,与那国岛附近方圆三英里的水域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}within three miles of Yonaguni Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是为航线的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could have to do with shipping routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,或者贸易战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the trade war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,柿子总是捡软的捏  所以他们对实力较弱的下手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't pick on the big kid, so they're picking on the little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎众议院所有的女性都支持这份法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost every woman in the House supports this bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而我不能成为其中之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can't be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果法案真能进入辩论 我不会单单退出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the bill goes to the floor as is, I won't just bow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会积极反对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll actively fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔说了些什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has Claire said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只是说你们之间有点磕磕绊绊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just that things have been a little rocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We saw someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指心理咨询师吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不担心被曝光吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weren't you worried about exposure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could put you in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么帮你忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统刚刚走进司法部大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Vice President just entered the Department of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现场请到的是艾拉·萨伊德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here with Ayla Sayyad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她发表在《华尔街电讯报》上的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whose Wall Street Telegraph article
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,直接促成了这次调查  艾拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}catalyzed the investigation. Ayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,关键问题在于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The issue at stake is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫是否也在某种程度上卷入其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether the White House was in any way involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有国外资金用于换取政治支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was foreign money traded for political favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又是否对外交关系产生影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did it influence diplomatic relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,单是为来自中国的政治献金洗白就是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the act of laundering Chinese contributions is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这笔钱对白宫决策产生影响的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it had a significant impact on White House policy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是更严重的罪行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's a far more serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾多次与丹尼尔·拉尼根会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've met with Daniel Lanagin on multiple occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  2003年起我们曾11次共处一室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were in the same room, yes, on 11 occasions since 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但其中我们交谈过的只有三次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we only spoke on three of those occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那几次已经标出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those instances are highlighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们谈了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那都是在筹款会上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, these were fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我对着几十号人发表演讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I speak to dozens of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有什么特定的话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}usually about nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是南方人  邓巴女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm southern, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈教导我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother taught me that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,席间讲话不仅礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}conversation during mealtime is not only polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有助消化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it aids the digestive process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那你没有跟他谈到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you didn't speak to him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿道希部落向这些超级政治行动委员会捐款的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the Adohi tribe's contributions to any of these super PACs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不和支持者提超级政治行动委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never discuss super PACs with any supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们熟悉法律规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both know the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在这些礼节性的谈话中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During one of these polite conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根先生可曾向你提起过冯山德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you recall Mr. Lanagin ever mentioning Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说过这个名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that name mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说除了铺天盖地的媒体报道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other than being plastered all over the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从这个角度说  就像我也听说过金·卡戴珊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that regard it means as much as Kim Kardashian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我再说得明确些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then let me be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你对冯先生涉及政治的活动有多少了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What knowledge do you have of Mr. Feng's political activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你丈夫的意思还是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this coming from your husband, or is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不是说我不再支持法案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's not that I don't support the bill anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是采访的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经答应让马特做专访了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've promised Matt an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那往后推几周吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe in a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等调查尘埃落定之后再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}once the investigation has died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,《纽约时代杂志》可不会干等着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The New York Times isn't going to wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经腾出十月份的封面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've already scheduled the cover for October.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于我们的安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on our timing --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就恕难参与了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I can't be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为嘉乐威的事  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the Galloway nonsense, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔  别这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你直说就行  我们是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can say so. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,的确影响不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会真相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't actually believe I --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但国内还是有不少人信的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But enough of the country still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特现在需要争取每一份支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Garrett needs every bit of support he can get right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那你心意已决了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So there's no convincing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽可能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll help as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄地帮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有传言说你和冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are rumors that you and Mr. Feng
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在去年五月的贸易峰会上进行了私下接触\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}served as back channels to the trade summit last May.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  就是"传言"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly. Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,峰会期间冯就在美国境内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have Feng in the U.S. during the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他做了私下接触\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if he was back-channeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and even if I were aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这种外交接触一般都是保密的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any form of diplomatic communication is usually classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你和总统说起过冯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever discussed Feng with the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,北京每一个权势人物我们都会说起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any major player in Beijing is worthy of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是承认了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是陈述一般情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a general comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你在能源危机期间与别人说起过他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you discuss him during the energy crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你是指跟他合资投资精炼厂的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assuming you're alluding to the refinery co-venture with --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我是指雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. With Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从来没聊起过精炼厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The refinery was never part of our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要的是能立即见效的方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We needed an immediate solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,建精炼厂在短期内什么都解决不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A refinery would have solved nothing in the short term.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而且据我所知  这交易最后黄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's my understanding that deal fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  但塔斯克拿到了补贴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Correct. But Tusk did receive a subsidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其他核电供应商也都拿到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As did every other nuclear energy provider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但他和冯有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But his connection with Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有钐补贴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then a subsidy on samarium --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没人从这笔补贴中获利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody made any profits off these subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,至多也就是保本而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At best they were breaking even.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  雷蒙德一开始还拒绝接受补贴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, Raymond fought us on the issue.
