Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这也怨不得她  这的确值得担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't blame her. It's a valid concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我不会谈嘉乐威的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him I won't engage on Galloway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以干脆也别问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so there's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是马特·贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Matt Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他要问什么我们说了不算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't dictate what he'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他肯定会问这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he will ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就说我不会回应这些无聊八卦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then I'll just say I won't answer tabloid questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个合理的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a legitimate question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,丑闻对选举有什么影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How the scandal could affect the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议我们也不做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I say you pull out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,取消掉整篇专题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We scrap the whole piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬在和我们对着干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie is fighting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,总统方面又指望不上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The leadership is noncommittal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要这篇专访让大家重新关注法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need this article to refocus attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但这于你不利啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it'll hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的形象和法案都不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both your personal image and the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们谁都不靠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we cut the cord,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,约好的两场采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we schedule two interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么取消了  马特不会生气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we cancel, won't Matt be furious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大家只会看到我们的退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The story will be about pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要权衡利弊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're talking about the lesser of two evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望你成为目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want you to become the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,使我们的努力白费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to undo all the work --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是我去呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what if it's not me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可你说第一夫人不打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you said the first lady wasn't going --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是她  是其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not her. Someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,建设大桥是否是换取切断共和党资助金的筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was the bridge a trade-off to prevent additional GOP funding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As far as I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这座大桥是总统在兑现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the bridge was a delivery on a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他对选民做出的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president had made to the voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还没问完吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we finished here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你会见过多少位国会议员  邓巴女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many members of Congress have you interviewed, Ms. Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,200吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,194位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}194.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I want to be of help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想前面194位都已经说得差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I doubt I can offer any more than the 194 that preceded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了一些有用的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have gotten some useful testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从谁那儿得来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,众议院高层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A high-ranking House member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,领导层的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃·博奇  杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch? Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人说他参加了7月14日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This individual says he attended a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在总统办公室的会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}July 14th in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她说是个男的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said "He,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么一定是博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it must have been Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德肯定能轻易收买他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure Raymond had no trouble buying him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你也参加了那次会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You attended that meeting also.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得那次会议的主题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you recall the subject of that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一波共和党的攻击广告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wave of conservative attack ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有足够财力与之抗衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were being outspent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很震惊吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must have been quite a shock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尼根转而把钱捐给了另一党派\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when Lanagin's tribe shifted contributions to the other party,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,之前他们从没给共和党捐过钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they hadn't given a single dime to the Republicans before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这的确会令我们震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it would have been a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们当时并不知道钱是哪来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we didn't know where the money was coming from at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,据我的线人说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to my source...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃·博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的线人说  当时预计有两千五百万\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My source says the estimate was 25 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,引用你说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said, and I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"凭空出现这么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"With this kind of influx,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有人违规了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can be sure somebody isn't playing by the rules."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,像是我说过的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like something I might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃的记性比我好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bob has a better memory than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,杰斐逊港大桥刚获批\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The money stopped just after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这笔钱就中断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真有想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a theory here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还是查不出头绪就瞎猜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or are you just grasping at straws?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大桥与冯有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bridge leads to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,冯与拉尼根和塔斯克有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng gives me Lanagin and Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克和总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk and the president --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴女士  你想玩六度分隔的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Dunbar, you want to play six degrees of separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还能扯上{\u1}吉米·霍法{\u0}和教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you could throw in Jimmy Hoffa and the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}82年神秘失踪的工会领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那么一度分隔如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then how about one degree of separation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,道格拉斯·斯坦普  你的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas Stamper, your chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是7月14日他在拉尼根的赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is him at Lanagin's casino July 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我用这些申请了搜查证  调出了飞行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used these to get a warrant for flight records.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天  斯坦普先生飞去北京\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next day, Mr. Stamper was on a flight to Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么去赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why was he at the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么去北京\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why was he in Beijing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想与委托人谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would like to speak to my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我很努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不拖泥带水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道重要的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what my priorities are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有这么个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's this -- this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在我的生活中  而是在我生活的边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not even in my life, except on the edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以界限很模糊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}making things blurrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不让我想喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't tempt me to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那感觉更像...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's more like she --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她给我的感觉就像我喝酒时的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's more like she feels what it was like when I was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,总是无法满足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I couldn't get enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我喝多少酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how many drinks I had,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,总是喝不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和她在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I -- I don't want to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I -- I -- I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她更像是我女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's more like she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道了  太乱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. This is fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该再跟她联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should cut her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像戒酒一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The way I did with booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些  说完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你与我们分享\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要一些时间回答你的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll need some time before responding to your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could wait as long as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能要花上一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,事关国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are national security matters at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统需要咨询顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president needs to consult with his advisors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}National security?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要用这招吗  奥利弗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you really gonna play that card, Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他的回答可能涉及保密信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His answers could entail classified material.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候能得到回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When can we expect a response?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会通知你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以拿走这些截屏照片吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May we hold onto the screen cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,请便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快联系你  邓巴女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be in touch soon, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要觉得我们在针对你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you think you're insulated, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们调查的不止道格拉斯·斯坦普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our investigation is much bigger than Douglas Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就到这儿吧  邓巴女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough, Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你的时间  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,乐意合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Happy to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,刚出虎口  又入狼窝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the lion's den to a pack of wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是滴血的肉  那就杀了别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you're fresh meat, kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们更新鲜的肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and throw them something fresher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是菲茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I'm Fitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要知道  你可以自己硬挺着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you know, uh, you can isolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,独自承担这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}white-knuckle this shit if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你也可以向他人求助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you can ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你有担保人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got a sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  都已经14年了  我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It's been 14 years. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,电话在背面  如果你改主意的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Number's on the back, if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你有司机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you had a driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望他听到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want him overhearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不该来这个州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't even be near this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去加州绕了点远路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long layover on my way to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,稽核员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got auditors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,和联邦探员都在我办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}federal agents in my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,查看每一份文件和档案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}going through every file, every document.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们连我的垃圾都翻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going through my god damn trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她传唤你就坚持保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just stick to the Fifth if she subpoenas you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么知道去查斯坦普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, how do they know to look for Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,专查那天的录像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To search the tapes on that exact day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱下结论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是要牺牲我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're throwing me under the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德才是对头  你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwood's the roadkill. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要搞垮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going to fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会找到办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而你已经预见到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你的家人会得到妥善安置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you and your family will be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经给我提供认罪条件了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're already offering me a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没被起诉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You haven't even been charged yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我合作的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你能少坐几年牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll do less time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的家人会一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but your family will have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等你出来他们还是一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll still have nothing when you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你作证指认雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You testify against Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he'll still walk
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们只有你的证词作证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because all they'll have is your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在你的证词没多少可信度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that doesn't count for much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他要是不害怕你就不会来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't be here if he wasn't afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我来不是因为他害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not here because he's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here because you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确定你不会做蠢事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want to make sure you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在反复和北京沟通后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After repeated conversations with Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们坚持他们的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they remain intractable in their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我今早命令一个航母战斗群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This morning I gave orders for a carrier group
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在冲绳海域重新部署\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to reposition near Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们的舰只不会直接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This won't put our ships in direct confrontation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和中国军舰对峙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the Chinese vessels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但又能把对方纳入航母空袭范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it will put them within reach of airstrikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天晚些时候会知会中国大使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be informing the Chinese ambassador later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会和五角大楼联合发表声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll release a statement in coordination with the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的钐储量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, our stockpiles of samarium
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最多能再坚持两个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will only last another two months at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we go this route --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道所有人的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I've -- I've heard everyone's concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is the decision I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,进行的怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有些问题需要后续澄清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a few follow-up questions that we have to address.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,比如什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么要紧的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, nothing major.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是零七碎八  一点细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just odds and ends. A few details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这调查会简短而温和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was under the impression this would be short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也以为  但她不依不饶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So was I, but she's very deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这事得尽快平息  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need this over, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,至少白宫需要这事尽快过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least as far as the White House is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't be distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是局势如此紧张的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with warships on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信马上就会结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm confident we're in the home stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去不像嘴上说得那么轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you seem more concerned than you're letting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不  完全没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搓手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're fidgeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的毕业戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my class ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I forget I --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它埋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I buried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I -- it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过你这么紧张  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never seen you this stressed before, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过你这么疲惫  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I've never seen you this tired before, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有自己的圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got rings of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,黑眼圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dark ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,越发明显了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, they're getting worse, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你该在总统办公室的沙发上多打打盹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should take more naps on those sofas in the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如今光打盹可管不了用了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, naps don't cut it these days, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都解不了乏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谎话连篇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lie after lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,先是对检察官  现在是对总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First to a prosecutor, then to a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到我全无防护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我手指上曾被戒指庇护的皮肤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like the skin where my ring used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,强如阿喀琉斯  也终被踵上一箭毙命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even Achilles was only as strong as his heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,道格在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他老不接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not answering his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他去参加互助会了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He went to a meeting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大白天的去干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在可能在往回赶了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he's on his way back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要他赶紧回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want him back now as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  这是给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, this arrived for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是雷米跳槽去格兰顿-希尔时你送给他的手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The watch you gave Remy when he left for Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我从手表背面的名言认出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I recognized it from the quote on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他留信息了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was there a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  只有这只表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Just the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧联系道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's find Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意塑料杯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive the plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吕克·图伊曼斯  他有真本事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luc Tuymans. He's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就信你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll take your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的  这些全都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not mine. None of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在加州  你要是想卖房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}California, you want to sell your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的房屋中介会先装修一番\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your realtor decorates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,起码会装个样板间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, one room at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算搬到哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我在索诺玛有座小农场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I have a little ranch in Sonoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My wife's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子也不和我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My kids won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我还有我的画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at least I'll have my painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你还画画吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不画  农场也是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. And there's no ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但其余的话  其余的都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the rest of it -- the rest of it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为杰奎琳·夏普而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here about Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在考虑雇用她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're thinking of hiring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,做说客吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lobbyist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能赢不了连任竞选了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She could lose her re-elect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在局势对在位者不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a great time to be an incumbent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你和她关系很近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you two are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你来是想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you're looking for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,推荐函吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是K街员工流动率最低的一家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have the lowest turnover of any shop on K Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}K街上有很多智囊公司  游说公司和倡导团体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在给格兰顿-希尔物色什么样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you looking for at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,心狠手辣  争强好胜的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A killer instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那你找她算是找对人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she certainly has that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me if I'm prying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不是她造成了你的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but did she have anything to do with your, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,出局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Departure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬做了她必须做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie did what she had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会原谅她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll never forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但我理解她为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I understand why she did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她究竟做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我用现金买的票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I paid cash for my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常谨慎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,显然不够谨慎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clearly not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  赌场里到处是摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, the casino had cameras everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本无法避开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was no way to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们的监控录像肯定有几千小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there had to have been thousands of hours of footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么找出来的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now how they found that --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有个问题我必须要问  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to ask you a question, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  但你要如实作答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm sorry, but I need you to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是又开始酗酒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想都没想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近的表现可很像喝醉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it would explain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全有权生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经顾不上生气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm more concerned than I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在需要你  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you now, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,非常需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都不年轻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦失败  都会老死在牢里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we fail, we'll die in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近不在状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't been myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你14年前也是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you said to me 14 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了你第二次机会  也收获了回报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I gave you a second chance, it paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你戒酒了  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got clean, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这份工作是我最看重的  先生  无比重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing means more to me than this job, sir. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要知道你能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know that it can be managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you need my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我会伸出援手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能自己解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,局面会好转的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things'll be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没给过别人第三次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never given someone a third chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我再给你一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你后悔的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请相信这一点  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please believe that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是雷米让他们找到录像的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was Remy who alerted them to the footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的离职礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His going-away gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,读读背面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Read the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他想传达什么信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think he's trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他  给我安排一次会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but track him down and set up a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴那边怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没法逃开事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't run from the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我说什么  我就说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll say whatever you want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我负全责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take responsibility for all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能会起诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She could indict you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,幕僚就是做这个的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what having a staff is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个更好的解决办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a better solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们一起承担责任    -怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We'll both take responsibility.   - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,后天和邓巴安排一次会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set up an interview with Dunbar. Day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们俩需要时间做足准备    -是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You and I need time to do our homework.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么时候弄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,密查姆帮我修好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meechum helped me fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不让我跑步  我总得想办法健身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they're not gonna let me run, I have to work out some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它搬上楼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You carried it all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,更隐秘  有人帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For privacy. I had help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-密查姆    -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Meechum.   - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他还真是样样通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's a jack of all trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-工匠  搬家具的    -肉盾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Handyman. Furniture mover.   - Human shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有多糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有证据证明道格出现在不该出现的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have evidence of Doug being where he shouldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,讲实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-你该不会真打算...    -不是全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're not actually gonna --   - Selectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不过绊了一下  还没摔倒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a stumble, not a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果只是绊一下  你不会这个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You aren't like this when it's just a stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么样子    -你害怕了  我看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Like how?   - You're scared. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,1分39秒划五百米  这是我的最佳成绩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}500 meters at 1:39. That was my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,以此为目标吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shoot for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}堕胎等于谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}堕胎伤害女性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}丢人  通奸者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-药挺有用的    -那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The meds are helping.   - Oh, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,街角那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those people at the end of the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,闹得挺厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一天到晚不消停  周末人数还翻番\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're there 24/7. Twice as many on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在都习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're so used to it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我能脱鞋吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I take off my shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得该穿得正式点  但我真不喜欢高跟鞋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I should dress up, but I am not good with heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,行  当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈说和裙子很搭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom said they went with the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道过去六个月很难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the last six months have been difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没能像预想的那样得到领导层的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just don't have the support that we expected in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也猜到你不会只是想问问我的近况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I figured this wasn't just about checking up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前改过主意  我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You changed your mind before, and I understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在你的情况似乎稳定多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now it seems as though things are more stable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you willing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都坐在你家了  说不有点过意不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard to say no when I'm in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听到了外头那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you hear those people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们声音很响  但我们要发出更高的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're loud, but I think we need to be louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但这声音不能是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it can't be my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经是婴儿杀手  和出轨者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I'm the baby killer, the cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这声音得是你发出的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It needs to be your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你没有污点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A clear voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在军事法庭上作证了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm already testifying at the court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但那里不对媒体开放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's closed to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事曾发生在很多人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are so many people this has happened to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么一定是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是你打来了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're the one who called.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算在麦金尼斯判刑之前发表吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna try to put it out before McGinnis gets sentenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯  有空吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth? You have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,马特  我一会儿打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Matt, I have to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,关门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统录用你的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the vice president brought you on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是反对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I advised against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不得不承认你干得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't deny you've done a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很注重保护副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm very protective of the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我很难跟旁人分担这份职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find it hard to share that duty with anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这也导致我可能出错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which leaves me open to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.08,0:24:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的缺点之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's one of my faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我跟副总统说的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I told the vice president,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道信任需要我自己争取\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand that trust is something that I need to earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我得到工作的途径不正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And given how I got the job --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果副总统信任你  那我就信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the vice president trusts you, then I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在是一个团队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're a team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我也没法孤军奋战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the truth is I can't do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要我做任何事都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything and everything you ask of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.28,0:24:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能与媒体无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might have nothing to do with the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.93,0:24:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,新闻发言人不过是个名号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Press Secretary is just a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有两个任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have two tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.47,0:24:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  给我找到雷米·丹顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First, find me Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.73,0:24:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But be discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.29,0:24:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其次  我要你去翻阅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Second, I need you to go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.25,0:24:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统的行程记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through the Vice President's travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,过去十年的所有记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything in the past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.59,0:24:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,任何软肋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything that could hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.86,0:24:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我从前往后找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll work forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.93,0:25:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你从后往前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You work backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,马上去办  还有道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on it. And Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.53,0:25:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}删除瑞秋?  删除
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.49,0:25:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,南茜  帮我订部新手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nancy, I need you to order me a new phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:26:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}追踪道格拉斯·斯坦普  删除联系人瑞秋  手机追踪中断
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.78,0:26:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你说是"零七碎八""马上就会结束"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said "Odds and ends." The "Home stretch."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.42,0:26:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我几个小时前才看到了这些内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was presented with this information just hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.62,0:26:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是能招致弹劾的罪行  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're talking about impeachable offenses, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.27,0:26:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不会  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.20,0:26:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的幕僚长...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Chief of Staff was --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.23,0:26:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时觉得赌场跟这事有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a gut feeling that the casino was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.07,0:26:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我派道格去查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sent Doug down there to get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.78,0:26:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一发现联系就该马上去找司法部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have taken this to the DOJ the first inkling you had --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时就不想那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what I didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,万一没有什么  我却制造事端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To create some ruckus if nothing was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.15,0:26:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能私自调查  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't go on conducting your own investigations, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.12,0:26:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,查明真相  尽职调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fact-finding, due diligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.59,0:26:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.17,0:26:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有任何违法行为  我必须知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If any laws were being broken, I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.65,0:26:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要这么跟邓巴说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's what you want to tell Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.79,0:26:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不透露我们的外交手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I didn't want to disclose our diplomatic protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心中期选举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I was concerned about the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.91,0:27:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想保护美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that I wanted to protect the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.77,0:27:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我做得不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, maybe what I did was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.59,0:27:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没干任何违法的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I didn't do anything illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.40,0:27:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟我的律师认真探讨过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've discussed this at length with my lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.26,0:27:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我们承认这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dunbar does not strike me as the sort of person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.05,0:27:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得邓巴也不会就此打住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who will put on the brakes, even if we admit all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,反而还可能促使她继续深挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, it might encourage her to dig deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.65,0:27:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我打算上交我全部的行程记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I want to hand over all of my travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你也该这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think you should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.05,0:27:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,自愿上交吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Volunteer them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.25,0:27:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  表示我们乐意合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. As a gesture of cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.83,0:27:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们表示做得够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Haven't we made enough gestures?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.48,0:27:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样她就不会那么叫劲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll take the wind outta her sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不想让她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't, uh, want her,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.18,0:27:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细查看我所有的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}uh, poring over every one of my comings and goings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.11,0:27:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在担心他的婚姻咨询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's worried about his marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.67,0:27:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他也该担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as he should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.37,0:27:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是在担心你的婚姻咨询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're worried about your marriage counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.00,0:27:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.83,0:27:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被外界知道  会造成多大影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine the fallout if the public were to find out that --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.81,0:27:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是大海里的一根针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A needle in a haystack,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.75,0:27:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是邓巴要找的那根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and not a needle that Dunbar is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.58,0:27:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经会见了一半的国会议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's interviewed half of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这女人是要见血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That woman's after blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是八卦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not for gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她真的起疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even if she does raise an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.69,0:27:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是去探望一位生病的朋友  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were visiting a sick friend, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.71,0:27:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  表面上是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, ostensibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.67,0:28:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这她没什么可说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she couldn't possibly find any fault with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.95,0:28:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,叫嘉利克过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like Galich in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.21,0:28:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不打扰了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you two talk privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.65,0:28:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候去见邓巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When are you seeing Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.00,0:28:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明天  这样你也有时间准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow, so you have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.68,0:28:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟比尔谈谈  回头找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll speak to Bill and get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.05,0:28:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他会建议你不要这么做  是他职责所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll advise you against it, which is his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.80,0:28:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我会强烈建议你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would just encourage you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.82,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想想政治而不是法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to think politics and not legalese.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.27,0:28:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,议员女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.38,0:28:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要投票给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should I vote for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  马克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's -- it's okay, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.40,0:28:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.56,0:28:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很疲惫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.09,0:28:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,忙了一天竞选吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long day on the campaign trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.32,0:28:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.06,0:28:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你没跟我说过哈维梅耶女儿的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never told me about Havemeyer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.15,0:28:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.50,0:28:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.32,0:28:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知道你常去探望她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not that you visited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.32,0:28:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是你泄露出去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you leaked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你大老远跑来加州就是为了问我这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came all the way to California to ask me about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.04,0:29:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是到了加州才知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came to California to find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.12,0:29:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我提出买下哈维梅耶的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I offered to buy Havemeyer's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但他就那么告诉我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he told me for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实忙了一天竞选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has been a long day on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.87,0:29:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不相上下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's still a close race.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要是选民知道你是怎么当上党鞭就不会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not if the voters know how you became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.50,0:29:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在威胁我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you honestly threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.99,0:29:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,安排和弗兰克的会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.97,0:29:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care what you talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.86,0:29:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是你单独一人  会面也有记录就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}long as you're alone and the meeting is on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.90,0:29:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你去和邓巴谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you're gonna sit down with Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.42,0:29:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经问完我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've already done my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.70,0:29:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她  是弗兰克逼你那么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her Frank grilled you on your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.73,0:29:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,作伪证吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perjure myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.97,0:29:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,保住你的位子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你说出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? Tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.44,0:29:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想想那会有什么后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think how that'd play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.21,0:29:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.31,0:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要为了弗兰克毁了自己吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd really toss yourself off a cliff for Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.14,0:29:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不效忠于弗兰克·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have zero allegiance for Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会受他操纵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't be manipulated by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.56,0:29:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我更不会被你操纵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I sure as fuck won't be manipulated by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.95,0:29:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是虚张声势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.44,0:30:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.41,0:30:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,关于什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不在乎我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How little I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.42,0:30:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那跟这个没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.63,0:30:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has everything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.83,0:30:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该觉得恶心  但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should feel disgusted, but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.26,0:30:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只是特别失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just supremely disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.82,0:30:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们十分钟前接到电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got the call 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.87,0:30:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,直接从白宫顾问那里打来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Direct from the White House counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,总统要上交一切吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President's turning over everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.84,0:30:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从他就职那天开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the day he took office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.93,0:30:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会包括他去拜访那位朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're sure this includes the visits to his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.66,0:30:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  安保人员全部出动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has to. It was full security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.11,0:30:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phenomenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有下手的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have something we can work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.78,0:30:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我的记录...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, as for my logs...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.10,0:30:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.28,0:30:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿生命打包票吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd bet your life on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.02,0:30:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.98,0:30:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.31,0:30:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经检查了两次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been through 'em twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.27,0:30:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,反复检查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}backward and forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.34,0:31:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的声明呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.52,0:31:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的收件箱里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In your inbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.72,0:31:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过了  塞斯干得很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked it over. Seth did a nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.32,0:31:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会面一结束我们就要把消息发布出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to go wide with this the moment the interview's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.19,0:31:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样邓巴如果打算发布什么消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that we beat Dunbar to the punch
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.49,0:31:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以先发制人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case she decides to release something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.25,0:31:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我会守在电脑前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be at my computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.99,0:31:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一收到道格的消息就按下"发送"键\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ready to press "Send" the moment I hear from Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.81,0:31:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩睡过觉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have either of you slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.02,0:31:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很清醒  全速运转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're awake. Fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.43,0:31:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你去洗个澡  换件衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take a shower and put on a fresh suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.60,0:31:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生  我们在那边见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. I'll see you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你有至少三小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have at least three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,打个盹吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.28,0:31:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在我办公室睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can use my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.40,0:31:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你作证的时候麦金尼斯将军就在法庭里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}General McGinnis was in the courtroom when you testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.08,0:31:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.50,0:31:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你私下见过他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had you seen him in person --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.52,0:31:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在他侵犯你之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, since he assaulted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.25,0:31:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what was that like?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.23,0:31:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么个不愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not fun how?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很难受  真的很难受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was hard. Really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.23,0:31:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.84,0:32:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意把文章的焦点转移到你身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I -- I agreed to change the focus of my piece to focus on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.27,0:32:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道这肯定很难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, you know, I know this has gotta be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.21,0:32:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to help me out a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.31,0:32:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.32,0:32:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很擅长这个  我很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not very good at this. I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你打电话去安德伍德夫人的访谈时挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seemed fine when you called into Mrs. Underwood's interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.34,0:32:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她在电话那头跟我在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was there with me on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.74,0:32:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的紧张情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.10,0:32:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道自从你被侵犯后  这一直是个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that's been an issue since the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那种防御心理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The defense brought up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.43,0:32:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,引起了情绪与精神的不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what they called emotional and mental instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.45,0:32:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总是那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.78,0:32:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被攻击的人会再次被攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The person who was attacked gets attacked all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.93,0:32:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我觉得愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It made me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,律师一直问我恐慌症的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lawyer kept coming after me about my panic attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和我的抗抑郁药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my antidepressants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.39,0:32:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只是紧紧盯着麦金尼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I just kept staring at McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让他知道我能承受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted him to see I could take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.60,0:32:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.67,0:32:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让他先转过脸去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to make him look away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.49,0:32:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.00,0:32:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  当听到我说他不只是侵犯我的身体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. When I said he did more than violate my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他还背叛了自己的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He betrayed his country.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.59,0:32:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了海军陆战队的声誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He robbed it of a good Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.42,0:32:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈谈国会正在谈论的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's talk about the Sexual Assault Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.86,0:33:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,性侵法案吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's in front of Congress right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.06,0:33:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有人提出了很强烈的反对意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know it's taken some significant opposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是另一个老兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}most notably from another veteran,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.99,0:33:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,杰奎琳·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.53,0:33:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说  她也背叛了自己的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, she's betraying her country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.17,0:33:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.56,0:33:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.21,0:33:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你多给我们几天时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for giving us a few extra days.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.14,0:33:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,耐心对我来说不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no problem being patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.14,0:33:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能因此得到坦率的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as long as it leads to forthright answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.15,0:33:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你继续等待了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't make you wait a moment longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.48,0:33:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以开始了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.97,0:33:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.54,0:33:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上就完事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're just finishing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.79,0:33:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think, Mr. Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.68,0:33:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,留着还是剃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep growing it or have it shaved?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.60,0:33:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还是留着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, I guess I'll keep growing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.11,0:33:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.89,0:33:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我把后面清理一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me just clean up the back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.20,0:33:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不了  麦克  让我们单独待会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Mack, if you'd give me a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.34,0:33:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.02,0:33:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大概十年前我在这里建造了这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had this place built down here about 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.97,0:33:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我厌倦了每两周都要开车穿过整个城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got tired of driving all the way across town every two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.72,0:33:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在坐个电梯就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's just an elevator ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真方便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.56,0:34:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道不方便的是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what isn't convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.25,0:34:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在我办公室里挤下八个律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cramming eight attorneys into my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.19,0:34:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不是为召集我律所所有合伙人准备的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was not designed for the entire partnership of my law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.17,0:34:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们比较担心拉尼根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're worried about Lanagin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点害怕  但他能挺住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a little shaky, but he'll hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.43,0:34:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.47,0:34:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,博奇出手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Birch delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.65,0:34:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴提出斯坦普的问题了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did Dunbar bring up Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.77,0:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,会面是闭门的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sessions are closed-door,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.06,0:34:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想她肯定会提的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can't imagine she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.52,0:34:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那可怜的哈维梅耶那边呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what about poor Havemeyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.07,0:34:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他在杰姬·夏普的事上对我们有帮助吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was he any help to us on Jackie Sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的犹豫说明进展不顺吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not take your hesitation as a promising sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我向来不喜欢让你失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never like disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.94,0:34:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么都不知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.10,0:34:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.58,0:34:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他是确实不知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, do you think that's because there's nothing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.13,0:34:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是他在保护她呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or because he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.73,0:34:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以再找一个别的议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can go to another congressman --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.64,0:34:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.68,0:34:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,必须是个曝光率高的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has to be somebody high-profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,领导层的人  才能引起轰动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}someone in the leadership who will make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.32,0:35:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那我再找找博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get back to Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.38,0:35:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,太明显了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他摆明了不会对弗兰克手软\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now that he's shown no sympathy for Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,算盘不能打得太响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This can't look orchestrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.19,0:35:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多线作战  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Multiple fronts, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.29,0:35:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得是杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has to be Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.00,0:35:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mack?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.04,0:35:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把头发弄完吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.13,0:35:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回去干活儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.33,0:35:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  老板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.30,0:35:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你也得去干活儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to get back to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.61,0:35:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说过的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.17,0:35:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们办成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.60,0:35:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前否认你是去私下接触的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You denied being a back channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.07,0:35:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我没否认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.27,0:35:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有证实  因为这是机密信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I chose not to confirm because it was classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.35,0:35:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的办公室一直否认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your office has consistently denied --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.93,0:35:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我让道格那么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I instructed Doug to do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.11,0:35:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的新闻部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}along with my communications department.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.16,0:35:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,私下接触如果公之于众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a back channel becomes public,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.03,0:35:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也就没什么用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it defeats its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.35,0:35:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,精心编造的谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An orchestrated deception --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.73,0:35:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不予置评\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we had refused to comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.05,0:35:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人们就会知道确有其事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would have suggested that it was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.61,0:35:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就会危及这一渠道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which would have endangered the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.22,0:35:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在没办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.38,0:35:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,冯先生目前在迪拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng is currently in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.07,0:35:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.62,0:35:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他因腐败指控畏罪潜逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's fleeing corruption charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.75,0:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是他第一次被指控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the first time he's been accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你的问题是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.18,0:35:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是他洗钱  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know he laundered the money, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.78,0:35:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到确凿证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.90,0:36:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只是迟早的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before I have the proof to substantiate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.49,0:36:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的问题就是  我再问一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So my question, which I am asking again,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.81,0:36:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时是否知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is whether you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.10,0:36:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就再回答一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I will repeat my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.78,0:36:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时并不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.01,0:36:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时的确觉得有点不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did sense that something was awry,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,道格知道我的担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Doug was aware of my concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.30,0:36:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得调查清楚是我的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I took it upon myself to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.45,0:36:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统并不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.91,0:36:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道他去赌场的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had no knowledge he was going to the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.05,0:36:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  但这并不代表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None. But that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不对我手下的行为负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't take full responsibility for my staff's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.65,0:36:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我责无旁贷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The buck stops with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.76,0:36:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那你发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.02,0:36:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没发现  没有非法行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. No illegal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.28,0:36:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不像你那么神通广大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have the same resources that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.84,0:36:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有所怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.74,0:36:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不立即联络国家印第安人博彩委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why didn't you go immediately to the NIGC,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.02,0:36:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,印第安人事务局  或者...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the BIA, the Department --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.34,0:36:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你得理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.32,0:36:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中期选举很吃力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're facing very difficult midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.29,0:36:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想为一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to bring attention
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.39,0:36:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有实据的判断而引发关注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to a series of allegations that may have no basis in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,或许这逻辑不是很合理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that may have been misguided logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是我当时的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's how I chose to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.48,0:36:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,错误全在我一个人头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mistake is mine and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.81,0:36:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟道格没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not Doug's.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.48,0:36:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然更算不到总统头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And certainly not the president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.88,0:36:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是说我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It shouldn't surprise you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.74,0:36:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到事情的全部  你不会意外吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I say it feels like I am not getting the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.13,0:37:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我打算把全部展示给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I'm prepared to give you the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.71,0:37:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利弗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.15,0:37:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫相信透明度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House believes in transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.65,0:37:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统全部个人出行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of the vice president's personal travel logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.65,0:37:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还包括我十年党鞭任期内的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the last 10 years since I became whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.33,0:37:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和总统就职后的所有记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As well as the president's since inauguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会面的对象和时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There should be no doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.30,0:37:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都没有任何问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as to whom we met with and when.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.57,0:37:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我很怀疑里面的内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am skeptical about what this contains.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.14,0:37:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这点我们也预料到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is what we anticipated
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.59,0:37:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以奥利弗会全程在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and why Oliver will walk you through anything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,陪你审查全部材料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you might need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.99,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全都在那儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你还有其他疑问或要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you have any questions or requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也愿意倾力协助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll be happy to facilitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.76,0:37:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始我很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, at first I was really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.99,0:37:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但我一进入状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then as soon as I started getting into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.24,0:37:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吐露心声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}starting speaking from my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.79,0:37:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都自然脱口而出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all these things poured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.40,0:37:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那些我一度想说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.86,0:37:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想说的都说出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I've been wanting to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.73,0:37:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯告诉我马特很满意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth told me that Matt was very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.04,0:37:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想做更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.03,0:37:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,做更多采访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More interviews?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.11,0:37:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,报刊采访  上电视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Articles. TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不论什么都可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.89,0:37:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.79,0:38:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这很好  梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's great, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.55,0:38:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你给我这个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for making me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.29,0:38:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说是迈了一大步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a big step for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.39,0:38:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要赶飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.58,0:38:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我做别的采访  我可以留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can stay longer, if you need me to do another.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.84,0:38:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你先回芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you head back to Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.47,0:38:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们制定好计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and as soon as we put a plan together
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.45,0:38:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再给你打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can give you a buzz?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.95,0:38:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我能喝杯水吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I get a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.55,0:38:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,自来水  还是瓶装的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tap is fine, or you want bottled --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.11,0:38:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.11,0:38:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,汉纳希女士的车准备好了  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got Ms. Hennessey's car ready, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.07,0:38:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.22,0:38:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你去机场接她时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she seem all right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.16,0:38:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you picked her up from the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.82,0:38:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.52,0:38:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定  正常吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.83,0:38:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  可以这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.16,0:38:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她情绪起伏很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's very up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.78,0:38:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,反复无常  容易激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very skittish and manic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.30,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她确实有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess she did seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.01,0:38:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没怎么交流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.59,0:38:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.19,0:38:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在外面等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.17,0:39:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.75,0:39:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.68,0:39:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.01,0:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,车在外面等着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The car is ready whenever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.70,0:39:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一路顺风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have a safe flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.72,0:39:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,保持联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.86,0:40:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我与邓巴女士的谈话卓有成效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just had a very productive interview with Ms. Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.98,0:40:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,发新闻稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send out the press release.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.90,0:40:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.77,0:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  我只是打碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm fine. I just dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.34,0:40:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.47,0:40:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  我可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, uh, it's fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.93,0:40:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我来  你光着脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I've got it. You're barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.24,0:40:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华  你真的不需要这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Edward, you don't have to. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.16,0:40:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,天  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.16,0:40:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.47,0:40:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找绷带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get some bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.69,0:40:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.46,0:40:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我坚持  别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I want to. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.96,0:40:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,目前的报导都是正面的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The coverage has been mostly positive so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.15,0:40:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴那边呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dunbar's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.60,0:40:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只说很期待对记录的审核\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All they've said is they look forward to reviewing the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.01,0:40:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有人提到道格吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any heat on Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.44,0:41:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.37,0:41:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人要求我发表评论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm getting a lot of requests for comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.66,0:41:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的个人行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I acted on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.05,0:41:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会全力配合司法部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I will fully cooperate with the Justice Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.65,0:41:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可以这么对外说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can put that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.45,0:41:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.54,0:41:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这或许会吸引更多注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might generate more interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.69,0:41:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,注意我  而不是副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On me. Not the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.26,0:41:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么情况我都能处理好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle whatever comes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.02,0:41:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.69,0:41:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把最新的剪报都打出来  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll print you out the most recent clips, too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要想办法对付邓巴吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I find a way to tip off Dunbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.42,0:41:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还是顺其自然吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let nature take its course.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.63,0:41:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚找到雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got a hold of Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.66,0:41:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just got back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.64,0:41:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.49,0:41:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你的安保队都安排好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've arranged everything with your detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.86,0:41:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've done good work, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.65,0:41:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.63,0:42:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}菲茨
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.19,0:42:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  这样好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. That's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.97,0:42:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.89,0:42:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我有点喝醉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I'm a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.25,0:42:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是你家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.02,0:42:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随心所欲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.94,0:43:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也该喝一杯酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have a glass of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.64,0:43:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  夫人  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that, ma'am, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.15,0:43:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经下班了  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're off your shift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.09,0:43:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.64,0:43:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不许说不喝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I won't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.21,0:43:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该把好东西浪费在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you shouldn't waste any of your good stuff on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.39,0:43:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实根本不懂品酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really know anything about wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.19,0:43:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那喝点波本威士忌怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then how about bourbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.74,0:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定想喝一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bet you like a little of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.76,0:43:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不介意能喝点波本威士忌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I definitely don't mind a bourbon from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.33,0:43:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就喝波本威士忌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then bourbon it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.94,0:43:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在很难找啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a tough man to track down these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.53,0:43:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到手表了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.02,0:43:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,变则善\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"To improve is to change."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.06,0:43:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,常变则至善\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"To perfect is to change often."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.59,0:43:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想要什么样的变化呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What sort of change are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.78,0:43:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让我有选择余地的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whichever leaves me options.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.46,0:44:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在格兰顿-希尔遇到麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trouble at Glendon Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.26,0:44:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,带薪休假  直到调查结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Paid leave till the investigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.89,0:44:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,至少是带薪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, at least you're being paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.81,0:44:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是终止我合伙人身份的第一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First step in terminating my partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.98,0:44:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事你也懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how things go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.01,0:44:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.06,0:44:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我洗不掉的污点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a stain I can't wash out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.54,0:44:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你在寻找就业机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're looking for career opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.50,0:44:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是要把自己整个卖给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not offering myself to you wholesale.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.61,0:44:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会继续跟你斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep fighting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.61,0:44:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是力度会小一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I can fight you less.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.99,0:44:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你说"小一点"的意思是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And by "less" you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.70,0:44:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让你痛  但不会让你完蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough to hurt, but not finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.14,0:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报  我在格兰顿-希尔之外也有前途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in return I have a future beyond Glendon Hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.59,0:44:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么样的前途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever that might look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.78,0:44:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你是要保持中立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you offer neutrality,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.24,0:44:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但最终会追随胜利者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you'll go with the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.36,0:44:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看着更厉害的人获胜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figure let the best man win.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you go down,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.47,0:44:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不会是因为我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it won't be because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.71,0:44:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经挺够意思了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.26,0:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.29,0:44:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,保险  没别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Insurance. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.30,0:44:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟杰姬有关吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it have anything to do with Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.50,0:45:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.67,0:45:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你已经收服了博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you've got Birch in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.28,0:45:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会选择乌麦克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Womack's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.45,0:45:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太亲密了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.22,0:45:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是杰奎琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Jacqueline...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.55,0:45:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这单纯是关于我的前途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about my future, pure and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.19,0:45:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.86,0:45:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,留着这块表吧  就当做诚意的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep the watch, as a token of good faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.78,0:45:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他虽然否认  但他在保护她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might deny it, but he's protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.61,0:45:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有意识到的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What he doesn't realize is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.04,0:45:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我比雷蒙德更不在乎杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have even less regard for Jackie than Raymond does.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.36,0:45:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.79,0:45:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,感情用事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heart can choke the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.25,0:45:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,理智就会受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when all its blood flows back unto itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.99,0:46:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"我不喜欢深色头发的女孩"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said, "I don't like brunettes."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.21,0:46:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我差点错过了派对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like I almost missed the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.19,0:46:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经下班了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm off the clock, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.36,0:46:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张  弗兰西斯  我打破了一个杯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, relax. Francis, I broke a glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.21,0:46:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华被一块碎片割伤了手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Edward cut his hand on a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.42,0:47:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.35,0:47:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给你换绷带了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.54,0:47:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把那个解下来  我去拿新的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take that off, and I'll get fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.56,0:47:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望您不要介意  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you don't mind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.68,0:47:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我下了班...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was off-duty --
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.56,0:47:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她有没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.66,0:47:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉了吗  有一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drunk? A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.45,0:47:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝了多少这东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many of these have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.61,0:47:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.32,0:47:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.07,0:47:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用你的杯子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.43,0:47:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,用吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.60,0:47:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,情况还行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.56,0:47:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,流了很多血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.91,0:47:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看上去那么糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.76,0:47:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,痛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.28,0:48:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了酒不那么痛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bourbon helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.09,0:48:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果痛你就说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you let me know if this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.77,0:48:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不痛  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not one bit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.54,0:50:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你头痛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.53,0:50:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.57,0:50:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,睡前吃了几片阿司匹林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Took a few aspirin before I went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.20,0:51:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.37,0:51:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡得可香了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I slept like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.00,0:51:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  你需要好好睡一觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. You needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.35,0:51:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.11,0:51:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.14,0:51:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有个地址老是出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one address keeps popping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.62,0:51:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.39,0:51:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.36,0:51:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  密查姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Morning, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.57,0:51:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Morning, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.27,0:51:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是美好的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a beautiful day.
